[
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66268_000002_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66268/4576_66268_000002_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "\"I am Gisli of the Shieldings: Otter sendeth me to the Hall Sun; but on the way I was to tell tidings to the Houses west of the Water: so have I done.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66268_000004_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66268/4576_66268_000004_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "But many of us know the thicket and its ways; so we made not the easy hard.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66268_000004_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66268/4576_66268_000004_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "I was near the War duke, for I know the thicket and am light foot: I am a bowman.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66268_000004_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66268/4576_66268_000004_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "I saw Thiodolf that he was unhelmed and bore no shield, nor had he any coat of fence; nought but a deer skin frock.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66268_000006_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66268/4576_66268_000006_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "But Gisli went on: \"Yet by his side was his mighty sword, and we all knew it for Throng plough, and were glad of it and of him and the unfenced breast of the dauntless.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66268_000006_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66268/4576_66268_000006_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "Six hours we went spreading wide through the thicket, not always seeing one another, but knowing one another to be nigh; those that knew the thicket best led, the others followed on.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66268_000006_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66268/4576_66268_000006_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "So we went till it was high noon on the plain and glimmering dusk in the thicket, and we saw nought, save here and there a roe, and here and there a sounder of swine, and coneys where it was opener, and the sun shone and the grass grew for a little space.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66268_000009_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66268/4576_66268_000009_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "\"As they stood there, not out of earshot of a man speaking in his wonted voice, our War duke made a sign to those about him, and we spread very quietly to the right hand and the left of him once more, and we drew as close as might be to the thicket's edge, and those who had bows the nighest thereto.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66268_000009_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66268/4576_66268_000009_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "Thus then we abided a while again; and again came the horn's voice; for belike they had no mind to come their ways covertly because of their pride.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66268_000010_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66268/4576_66268_000010_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "\"Soon therewithal comes Fox creeping back to us, and I saw him whisper into the ear of the War duke, but heard not the word he said.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66268_000010_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66268/4576_66268_000010_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "I saw that he had hanging to him two Roman saxes, so I deemed he had slain those two, and so escaped the romans.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66268_000010_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66268/4576_66268_000010_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "Maidens, it were well that ye gave me to drink again, for I am weary and my journey is done.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66268_000011_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66268/4576_66268_000011_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "So again they brought him the horn, and made much of him; and he drank, and then spake on.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66268_000013_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66268/4576_66268_000013_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "\"But when they came into the lawn they spread out somewhat to their left hands, that is to say on the west side, for that way was the clear glade; but on the east the thicket came close up to them and edged them away. Therein lay the Goths.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66268_000014_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66268/4576_66268_000014_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "\"There they stayed awhile, and spread out but a little, as men marching, not as men fighting.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66268_000014_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66268/4576_66268_000014_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "With these Goths had the captain some converse, and presently he cried out two or three words of Welsh in a loud voice, and the nine men who were ahead shifted them somewhat away from us to lead down the glade westward.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66268_000021_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66268/4576_66268_000021_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "\"Such then was the battle in Mirkwood.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66268_000022_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66268/4576_66268_000022_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "So they brought him the horn, and he waved it over his head and drank again and spake:",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66268_000023_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66268/4576_66268_000023_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "\"Sixty and three dead men of the romans we counted there up and down that oak glade; and we cast earth over them; and three dead dastards of the Goths, and we left them for the wolves to deal with.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66268_000023_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66268/4576_66268_000023_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "And twenty five men of the romans we took alive to be for hostages if need should be, and these did we Shielding men, who are not very many, bring aback to the wain burg; and the Daylings, who are a great company, were appointed to enter the wood and be with Thiodolf; and me did Otter bid to bear the tidings, even as I have told you.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66268_000023_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66268/4576_66268_000023_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "And I have not loitered by the way.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66268_000024_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66268/4576_66268_000024_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "Then they fell to and spread the feast in the hall; and they ate and drank and were merry.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66268_000025_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66268/4576_66268_000025_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "So they went their ways, down the water: one pair went on the western side, and the other crossed Mirkwood water at the shallows (for being Midsummer the water was but small), and went along the east side, so that all the kindred might know of the tidings and rejoice.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66268_000026_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66268/4576_66268_000026_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "But when they sought for her on all sides she was not to be found, nor could anyone remember seeing her depart from the Hall.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66268_000026_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66268/4576_66268_000026_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "But this had they no call to heed, and the feast ended, as it began, in great glee.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66270_000003_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66270/4576_66270_000003_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "But as they were at the point of going she called to them, and said:",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66270_000005_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66270/4576_66270_000005_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "So they all gathered thereto, and she stood in her place and spake.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66270_000006_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66270/4576_66270_000006_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "\"Women and elders of the Wolfings, is it so that I spake somewhat of tidings last night?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66270_000008_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66270/4576_66270_000008_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "She said, \"And was it a word of victory?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66270_000009_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66270/4576_66270_000009_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "They answered \"yea\" again.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66270_000010_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66270/4576_66270_000010_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "\"Good is that,\" she said; \"doubt ye not!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66270_000010_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66270/4576_66270_000010_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "there is nought to unsay.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66270_000010_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66270/4576_66270_000010_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "But hearken!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66270_000011_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66270/4576_66270_000011_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "\"Yea, yea,\" they said, \"so will we.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66270_000017_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66270/4576_66270_000017_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "\"Now fear ye not, but pluck up a heart!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66270_000025_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66270/4576_66270_000025_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "But the others would turn to their day's work, and would go about their divers errands.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66270_000026_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66270/4576_66270_000026_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "For by that way also may peril come.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66270_000027_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66270/4576_66270_000027_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "Then smiled some of the bystanders, and the Hall Sun said: \"Good is it when the thought of a friend stirreth betimes in one's own breast.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66270_000028_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66270/4576_66270_000028_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "Wend we now to the Speech Hill.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66270_000030_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66270/4576_66270_000030_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "But the men folk gave all their ears to hearkening, and stood as close as they might.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66270_000031_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66270/4576_66270_000031_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "Then Egil clomb the Speech Hill, and said.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66274_000000_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66274/4576_66274_000000_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "CHAPTER eighteen-TIDINGS BROUGHT TO THE WAIN BURG",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66274_000001_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66274/4576_66274_000001_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "Now it must be told of Otter and they of the Wain burg how they had the tidings of the overthrow of the romans on the Ridge, and that Egil had left them on his way to Wolf stead.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66274_000003_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66274/4576_66274_000003_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "Men were peaceful and happy, for the time was fair and calm, and, as aforesaid, they dreaded not the Roman Host any more than if they were Gods dwelling in God home.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66274_000005_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66274/4576_66274_000005_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "So men made way before the grey horse, and its rider, and the horse was much spent and travel worn.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66274_000007_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66274/4576_66274_000007_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "He had many a time been in the Wolfing Hall, so he knew her at once and said:",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66274_000009_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66274/4576_66274_000009_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "She said: \"I fare as the bearer of evil tidings.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66274_000011_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66274/4576_66274_000011_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "Therewith he led her to a grassy knoll that was hard by, and set her down thereon and himself beside her, and said:",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66274_000013_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66274/4576_66274_000013_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "And methinks she has had some vision of their ways, though mayhap not altogether clear.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66274_000016_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66274/4576_66274_000016_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "But she escaped and so came to the others on the skirts of the thicket, having left of her skin and blood on many a thornbush and rock by the way.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66274_000021_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66274/4576_66274_000021_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "With that word she cast herself down on the grass by the mound side, and was presently asleep, for she was very weary.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66274_000024_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66274/4576_66274_000024_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "\"But know ye that the romans shall fall with all their power on the Wolfing dwellings, deeming that when they have that, they shall have all that is ours with ourselves also.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66274_000025_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66274/4576_66274_000025_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "\"So do ye order yourselves according to your kindreds, and let the Shieldings lead.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66274_000025_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66274/4576_66274_000025_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "Make no more delay!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66274_000025_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66274/4576_66274_000025_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "Geirbald, I see thee; come hither!\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66274_000026_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66274/4576_66274_000026_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "Lo thou, my ring for a token!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66274_000026_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66274/4576_66274_000026_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "Tarry not, nor rest till thy word be said!\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66274_000027_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66274/4576_66274_000027_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "Then turned Geirbald to find Viglund who was anigh to him, and he took the ring, and the twain went their ways without more ado, and rode into the wild wood.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66275_000004_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66275/4576_66275_000004_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "Of Geirbald and Viglund the tale tells that they rode the woodland paths as speedily as they might.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66275_000005_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66275/4576_66275_000005_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "\"Hail fellows! what tidings are toward?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66275_000009_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66275/4576_66275_000009_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "Now for your tidings, fellows.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66275_000012_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66275/4576_66275_000012_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "Our coming shall make him the speedier, and the less like to turn back if any alien band shall follow after him.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66275_000016_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66275/4576_66275_000016_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "Hearken, Viglund!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66275_000018_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66275/4576_66275_000018_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "\"Farewell,\" said he, \"and thou, Viglund, take this word in parting, that belike thou shalt yet see the romans, and strike a stroke, and maybe be smitten.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66275_000018_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66275/4576_66275_000018_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "For indeed they be most mighty warriors.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66275_000019_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66275/4576_66275_000019_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "Then made they no delay but rode their ways either side.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66275_000019_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66275/4576_66275_000019_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "And Geirbald and Viglund rode over rough and smooth all night, and were out of the thick wood by day dawn: and whereas they rode hard, and Viglund knew the ways well, they came to Mirkwood water before the day was old, and saw that the host was stirring, but not yet on the way.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66275_000020_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66275/4576_66275_000020_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "Nor may we tarry one minute ere we have seen Thiodolf.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66275_000021_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66275/4576_66275_000021_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "Said Wolfkettle, \"We will lead you to him; he is on the east side of the water, with all his host, and they are hard on departing.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66275_000023_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66275/4576_66275_000023_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "But as they rode amidst the clear water Wolfkettle lifted up his voice and sang:",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66275_000025_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66275/4576_66275_000025_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "They were in mid stream now, for the water was wide there; on the eastern bank were the warriors gathering, for they had beheld the faring of those men, and the voice of Wolfkettle came to them across the water, so they deemed that great tidings were toward, and would fain know on what errand those were come.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66275_000028_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66275/4576_66275_000028_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "The man who had ridden behind Viglund slipped off on to the ground; but Wolfkettle abode in his place behind Geirbald.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66275_000030_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66275/4576_66275_000030_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "The ragged cloud had drifted down south-east now and the rain fell no more, but the sun was still pale and clouded.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4576_66275_000031_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4576/66275/4576_66275_000031_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4576",
        "content": "Then Thiodolf looked gravely on them, and spake:",
